(Horns honking)

01:09:50.895 --> 01:09:53.229
(Tyres screeching)

01:09:53.314 --> 01:09:55.315
- Shit!
- (Horn honking)

01:09:59.987 --> 01:10:01.946
Oh, come on!

01:11:29.368 --> 01:11:32.537
Do you want to put
that cigarette out?

01:11:32.621 --> 01:11:34.872
- Why?
- You're in a church.

01:11:34.915 --> 01:11:37.125
You a priest?

01:11:37.209 --> 01:11:39.794
- What's your name?
- Mary.

01:11:48.429 --> 01:11:50.430
Is that better?

01:11:51.598 --> 01:11:53.516
What's your name, Father?

01:11:53.600 --> 01:11:55.852
- George.
- Father George.

01:13:14.681 --> 01:13:16.682
(Man)
Yes? Who is this?

01:13:16.767 --> 01:13:19.310
- (Knocking)
- (Deadbolt turning)

01:13:20.396 --> 01:13:23.231
- Ahh...
- Simone? Jesus Christ!

01:13:23.315 --> 01:13:25.483
- (Muffled shouting)
- (Man) Get out of here!

01:13:25.526 --> 01:13:28.736
- Shut up, you fucking pervert!
- This is a... ow!

01:13:28.821 --> 01:13:30.738
- This is a private room!
- (Muffled shouting)

01:13:30.823 --> 01:13:33.282
- What in the bleedin' hell's goin' on here?
- Get out, George!

01:13:33.367 --> 01:13:36.869
- He's tied you to the bleedin' bed!
- Give him his glasses!

01:13:36.954 --> 01:13:39.122
- You said you were respectable.
- I am fucking respectable!

01:13:39.206 --> 01:13:41.332
- You bloody bitch, you!
- You watch your fuckin' language!

01:13:41.417 --> 01:13:44.669
- George! Stop it, George!
- (George) What's the matter with you?

01:13:44.711 --> 01:13:46.671
- (Man) Get off!
- George!

01:13:46.713 --> 01:13:49.215
- You'd have done well in fuckin' Auschwitz!
- George!

01:13:49.299 --> 01:13:51.384
You old git!

01:13:52.803 --> 01:13:55.680
What in the bleedin' hell is this?

01:13:55.764 --> 01:13:58.182
You do this all the time, do you?

01:14:02.896 --> 01:14:05.690
What made you come here?
Curiosity?

01:14:08.819 --> 01:14:10.736
I found her.

01:14:13.031 --> 01:14:14.991
Where?

01:14:16.326 --> 01:14:18.995
Put your clothes on.
Make yourself respectable.

01:14:21.874 --> 01:14:25.084
- Where is she?
- She's with your mate.

01:14:25.169 --> 01:14:27.503
- Just a minute!
What the hell is going on here?

01:14:27.588 --> 01:14:29.547
- Get off!
- What do you think you're doing?

01:14:29.631 --> 01:14:31.716
- (Shouting)
- Don't you touch me!

01:14:31.800 --> 01:14:34.552
I want to look in your bag
and see what you got in there!

01:14:34.636 --> 01:14:37.597
- Jesus... you fucking...
- Get out of here!

01:14:39.349 --> 01:14:41.767
- Bloody... Get after that black...
- Please, get the police.

01:14:43.604 --> 01:14:46.772
- Jesus, what was that? What?
- Mace. Mace!

01:14:46.857 --> 01:14:49.275
Christ, you don't
need anybody, do ya?

01:14:49.359 --> 01:14:51.444
I do. I need you.

01:14:51.528 --> 01:14:54.280
So where is she?

01:14:54.364 --> 01:14:56.699
- She's with your friend Anderson.
- You've seen her?

01:14:56.783 --> 01:14:59.744
In a church.
What'd he meet her in a church for?

01:14:59.828 --> 01:15:02.413
It's the one place no one ever goes.

01:15:04.583 --> 01:15:06.542
So where do you want to go?

01:15:08.212 --> 01:15:10.838
Home.

01:15:10.923 --> 01:15:13.341
It's all right. Don't worry.

01:15:27.773 --> 01:15:29.690
You rushing off?

01:15:29.775 --> 01:15:32.443
- Where am I gonna rush to?
- Come on up, then.

01:15:53.423 --> 01:15:55.424
Haven't you
someone to rush to?

01:15:55.509 --> 01:15:57.510
You know I haven't.

01:15:58.887 --> 01:16:02.139
- Everyone should have.
- Well, you haven't.

01:16:02.224 --> 01:16:05.142
I'm different.

01:16:05.185 --> 01:16:07.270
How?

01:16:07.354 --> 01:16:09.313
How are you different?

01:16:10.482 --> 01:16:12.441
I'm the girl they rush home from.

01:16:18.532 --> 01:16:21.158
Yeah.

01:16:23.662 --> 01:16:25.705
- Simone.
- Simone!

01:16:25.789 --> 01:16:29.333
(Simone screaming)

01:16:29.418 --> 01:16:33.004
(Anderson laughing)

01:16:33.088 --> 01:16:35.506
My fuckin' arm!

01:16:40.554 --> 01:16:42.513
(Simone screaming)

01:16:44.933 --> 01:16:48.769
(Anderson, George shouting)

01:17:01.366 --> 01:17:03.784
(George)
Push the button.

01:17:42.658 --> 01:17:44.659
- Ow!
- Are you all right?

01:17:44.743 --> 01:17:46.744
Yeah, yeah.

01:17:48.789 --> 01:17:51.374
Jesus, you know
some nice people.

01:17:51.458 --> 01:17:55.586
- He knows where I live, George.
- Shut up!

01:17:55.671 --> 01:17:58.255
Calm down. Get your keys out.
Come on.

01:18:00.801 --> 01:18:03.803
Here, do us a favour.
Scratch my nose.

01:18:28.662 --> 01:18:31.580
- You're good at this too, eh?
- I'm good at most things.

01:18:34.334 --> 01:18:37.253
- You think he'll be back?
- I don't want to think about it.

01:18:39.047 --> 01:18:41.006
You better come
and stay with me.

01:18:46.304 --> 01:18:49.515
- Where is this?
- My friend Thomas's place.

01:18:49.599 --> 01:18:51.600
He likes detective stories.

01:18:54.354 --> 01:18:57.481
Don't you, Thomas?
Eh? Don't worry.

01:18:57.566 --> 01:18:59.984
- The dwarf did it again.
- What dwarf?

01:19:00.068 --> 01:19:02.319
There's a dwarf who's been
murderin' opera singers.

01:19:02.404 --> 01:19:04.405
- Why don't you tell her?
- Aye, that's right.

01:19:04.489 --> 01:19:06.449
Apparently this dwarf's
been bumpin' off...

01:19:06.533 --> 01:19:08.534
Sorry. I didn't introduce you.

01:19:08.618 --> 01:19:11.036
Thomas, this is Simone.

01:19:11.121 --> 01:19:13.456
- How do you do, Simone?
- Pleased to meet you, Thomas.

01:19:13.540 --> 01:19:16.333
- Excuse the hands, eh?
- No problem.

01:19:16.418 --> 01:19:21.714
(Thomas) Sorry about the mess. Just move
them carburettors and have a seat.

01:20:46.341 --> 01:20:51.303
♪ (Opera playing on stereo)

01:21:44.149 --> 01:21:47.484
♪ (Opera continues)

01:21:57.537 --> 01:21:59.496
Didn't you like that?

01:22:03.793 --> 01:22:07.254
No. You didn't, did you?

01:22:11.384 --> 01:22:15.220
- You're the priest.
- That's right. Father George.

01:22:15.305 --> 01:22:18.223
Well, you weren't meant to.

01:22:23.229 --> 01:22:25.731
Where's your clothes?

01:22:35.784 --> 01:22:39.078
- Why are you here?
- Simone sent me.

01:22:39.162 --> 01:22:42.790
Remember Simone?
Come on.

01:22:50.924 --> 01:22:52.883
Get on my back.

01:23:02.936 --> 01:23:04.937
What'd you do to her, eh?

01:23:05.021 --> 01:23:07.064
- What'd you do to her?
- Nothing.

01:23:08.608 --> 01:23:11.568
Don't worry, sir.
I'll take care of it for you.

01:23:29.587 --> 01:23:32.548
♪ Wind came out
and blew them in again

